{
  "video_id": "H_pqhMO3ZSY",
  "title": "What will a future without secrets look like? | Alessandro Acquisti",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12641.0,
      "end_time": 14995.0,
      "text": "I would like to tell you a story"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14995.0,
      "end_time": 18171.0,
      "text": "connecting the notorious privacy incident"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18171.0,
      "end_time": 20939.0,
      "text": "involving Adam and Eve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20940.0,
      "end_time": 24386.0,
      "text": "and the remarkable shift in the boundaries"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24386.0,
      "end_time": 27720.0,
      "text": "between public and private which has occurred"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27720.0,
      "end_time": 28842.0,
      "text": "in the past 10 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28842.0,
      "end_time": 30140.0,
      "text": "You know the incident."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30140.0,
      "end_time": 33470.0,
      "text": "Adam and Eve one day in the Garden of Eden"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33470.0,
      "end_time": 35313.0,
      "text": "realize they are naked."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35313.0,
      "end_time": 36813.0,
      "text": "They freak out."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 36813.0,
      "end_time": 39570.0,
      "text": "And the rest is history."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39570.0,
      "end_time": 41758.0,
      "text": "Nowadays, Adam and Eve"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41758.0,
      "end_time": 44119.0,
      "text": "would probably act differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44119.0,
      "end_time": 46387.0,
      "text": "[@Adam Last nite was a blast! loved dat apple LOL]"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 46387.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "[@Eve yep.. babe, know what happened to my pants tho?]"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 50896.0,
      "text": "We do reveal so much more information"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50896.0,
      "end_time": 54230.0,
      "text": "about ourselves online than ever before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 54230.0,
      "end_time": 55934.0,
      "text": "and so much information about us"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 55934.0,
      "end_time": 58158.0,
      "text": "is being collected by organizations."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 58158.0,
      "end_time": 61440.0,
      "text": "Now there is much to gain and benefit"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61440.0,
      "end_time": 63885.0,
      "text": "from this massive analysis of personal information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63886.0,
      "end_time": 65832.0,
      "text": "or big data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 65832.0,
      "end_time": 68470.0,
      "text": "but there are also complex tradeoffs that come"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68470.0,
      "end_time": 71568.0,
      "text": "from giving away our privacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 71568.0,
      "end_time": 75591.0,
      "text": "And my story is about these tradeoffs."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75591.0,
      "end_time": 78175.0,
      "text": "We start with an observation which, in my mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78175.0,
      "end_time": 81502.0,
      "text": "has become clearer and clearer in the past few years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81502.0,
      "end_time": 83598.0,
      "text": "that any personal information"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83599.0,
      "end_time": 85884.0,
      "text": "can become sensitive information."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85884.0,
      "end_time": 90900.0,
      "text": "Back in the year 2000, about 100 billion photos"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 90900.0,
      "end_time": 91921.0,
      "text": "were shot worldwide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 91921.0,
      "end_time": 94986.0,
      "text": "but only a minuscule proportion of them"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 94986.0,
      "end_time": 96869.0,
      "text": "were actually uploaded online."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 96869.0,
      "end_time": 100230.0,
      "text": "In 2010, only on Facebook, in a single month,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 100230.0,
      "end_time": 103500.0,
      "text": "2.5 billion photos were uploaded,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 103500.0,
      "end_time": 105382.0,
      "text": "most of them identified."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 105382.0,
      "end_time": 107262.0,
      "text": "In the same span of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 107262.0,
      "end_time": 112132.0,
      "text": "computers&#39; ability to recognize people in photos"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 112132.0,
      "end_time": 115740.0,
      "text": "improved by three orders of magnitude."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 115740.0,
      "end_time": 117622.0,
      "text": "What happens when you combine"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 117622.0,
      "end_time": 119123.0,
      "text": "these technologies together:"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 119123.0,
      "end_time": 121781.0,
      "text": "increasing availability of facial data;"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 121781.0,
      "end_time": 125429.0,
      "text": "improving facial recognizing ability by computers;"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 125429.0,
      "end_time": 127611.0,
      "text": "but also cloud computing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 127611.0,
      "end_time": 129499.0,
      "text": "which gives anyone in this theater"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 129499.0,
      "end_time": 131590.0,
      "text": "the kind of computational power"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 131590.0,
      "end_time": 132945.0,
      "text": "which a few years ago was only the domain"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 132945.0,
      "end_time": 134727.0,
      "text": "of three-letter agencies;"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 134727.0,
      "end_time": 136105.0,
      "text": "and ubiquitous computing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 136105.0,
      "end_time": 138997.0,
      "text": "which allows my phone, which is not a supercomputer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 138997.0,
      "end_time": 140668.0,
      "text": "to connect to the Internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 140668.0,
      "end_time": 143200.0,
      "text": "and do there hundreds of thousands"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 143200.0,
      "end_time": 145641.0,
      "text": "of face metrics in a few seconds?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 145641.0,
      "end_time": 148269.0,
      "text": "Well, we conjecture that the result"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 148269.0,
      "end_time": 150333.0,
      "text": "of this combination of technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 150333.0,
      "end_time": 153221.0,
      "text": "will be a radical change in our very notions"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 153221.0,
      "end_time": 155478.0,
      "text": "of privacy and anonymity."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 155478.0,
      "end_time": 157471.0,
      "text": "To test that, we did an experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 157471.0,
      "end_time": 159592.0,
      "text": "on Carnegie Mellon University campus."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 159592.0,
      "end_time": 161691.0,
      "text": "We asked students who were walking by"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 161691.0,
      "end_time": 163470.0,
      "text": "to participate in a study,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 163470.0,
      "end_time": 166320.0,
      "text": "and we took a shot with a webcam,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 166320.0,
      "end_time": 168814.0,
      "text": "and we asked them to fill out a survey on a laptop."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 168814.0,
      "end_time": 170793.0,
      "text": "While they were filling out the survey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 170793.0,
      "end_time": 173590.0,
      "text": "we uploaded their shot to a cloud-computing cluster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 173590.0,
      "end_time": 175317.0,
      "text": "and we started using a facial recognizer"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 175317.0,
      "end_time": 177722.0,
      "text": "to match that shot to a database"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 177722.0,
      "end_time": 180115.0,
      "text": "of some hundreds of thousands of images"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 180115.0,
      "end_time": 183711.0,
      "text": "which we had downloaded from Facebook profiles."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 183711.0,
      "end_time": 186970.0,
      "text": "By the time the subject reached the last page"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 186970.0,
      "end_time": 190317.0,
      "text": "on the survey, the page had been dynamically updated"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 190317.0,
      "end_time": 192630.0,
      "text": "with the 10 best matching photos"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 192630.0,
      "end_time": 194915.0,
      "text": "which the recognizer had found,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 194915.0,
      "end_time": 196653.0,
      "text": "and we asked the subjects to indicate"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 196653.0,
      "end_time": 200773.0,
      "text": "whether he or she found themselves in the photo."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 200773.0,
      "end_time": 204472.0,
      "text": "Do you see the subject?"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 204472.0,
      "end_time": 207317.0,
      "text": "Well, the computer did, and in fact did so"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 207317.0,
      "end_time": 209466.0,
      "text": "for one out of three subjects."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 209466.0,
      "end_time": 212650.0,
      "text": "So essentially, we can start from an anonymous face,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 212650.0,
      "end_time": 216134.0,
      "text": "offline or online, and we can use facial recognition"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 216134.0,
      "end_time": 218494.0,
      "text": "to give a name to that anonymous face"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 218494.0,
      "end_time": 220602.0,
      "text": "thanks to social media data."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 220602.0,
      "end_time": 222474.0,
      "text": "But a few years back, we did something else."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 222474.0,
      "end_time": 224297.0,
      "text": "We started from social media data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 224297.0,
      "end_time": 227347.0,
      "text": "we combined it statistically with data"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 227348.0,
      "end_time": 229450.0,
      "text": "from U.S. government social security,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 229450.0,
      "end_time": 232774.0,
      "text": "and we ended up predicting social security numbers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 232774.0,
      "end_time": 234286.0,
      "text": "which in the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 234286.0,
      "end_time": 236326.0,
      "text": "are extremely sensitive information."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 236326.0,
      "end_time": 238418.0,
      "text": "Do you see where I&#39;m going with this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 238419.0,
      "end_time": 241341.0,
      "text": "So if you combine the two studies together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 241341.0,
      "end_time": 242853.0,
      "text": "then the question becomes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 242853.0,
      "end_time": 245573.0,
      "text": "can you start from a face and,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 245573.0,
      "end_time": 247884.0,
      "text": "using facial recognition, find a name"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 247884.0,
      "end_time": 250553.0,
      "text": "and publicly available information"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 250553.0,
      "end_time": 252484.0,
      "text": "about that name and that person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 252485.0,
      "end_time": 254733.0,
      "text": "and from that publicly available information"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 254733.0,
      "end_time": 256774.0,
      "text": "infer non-publicly available information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 256774.0,
      "end_time": 258380.0,
      "text": "much more sensitive ones"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 258380.0,
      "end_time": 259873.0,
      "text": "which you link back to the face?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 259873.0,
      "end_time": 261789.0,
      "text": "And the answer is, yes, we can, and we did."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 261789.0,
      "end_time": 264357.0,
      "text": "Of course, the accuracy keeps getting worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 264357.0,
      "end_time": 265301.0,
      "text": "[27% of subjects&#39; first 5 SSN digits identified (with 4 attempts)]"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 265301.0,
      "end_time": 269128.0,
      "text": "But in fact, we even decided to develop an iPhone app"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 269128.0,
      "end_time": 271842.0,
      "text": "which uses the phone&#39;s internal camera"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 271843.0,
      "end_time": 273443.0,
      "text": "to take a shot of a subject"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 273443.0,
      "end_time": 274930.0,
      "text": "and then upload it to a cloud"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 274930.0,
      "end_time": 277592.0,
      "text": "and then do what I just described to you in real time:"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 277592.0,
      "end_time": 279680.0,
      "text": "looking for a match, finding public information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 279680.0,
      "end_time": 281410.0,
      "text": "trying to infer sensitive information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 281410.0,
      "end_time": 284100.0,
      "text": "and then sending back to the phone"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 284100.0,
      "end_time": 287609.0,
      "text": "so that it is overlaid on the face of the subject,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 287610.0,
      "end_time": 289511.0,
      "text": "an example of augmented reality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 289511.0,
      "end_time": 291962.0,
      "text": "probably a creepy example of augmented reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 291962.0,
      "end_time": 295301.0,
      "text": "In fact, we didn&#39;t develop the app to make it available,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 295301.0,
      "end_time": 297223.0,
      "text": "just as a proof of concept."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 297223.0,
      "end_time": 299536.0,
      "text": "In fact, take these technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 299536.0,
      "end_time": 301373.0,
      "text": "and push them to their logical extreme."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 301373.0,
      "end_time": 304920.0,
      "text": "Imagine a future in which strangers around you"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 304920.0,
      "end_time": 306402.0,
      "text": "will look at you through their Google Glasses"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 306403.0,
      "end_time": 308710.0,
      "text": "or, one day, their contact lenses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 308710.0,
      "end_time": 312729.0,
      "text": "and use seven or eight data points about you"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 312730.0,
      "end_time": 315312.0,
      "text": "to infer anything else"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 315312.0,
      "end_time": 317915.0,
      "text": "which may be known about you."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 317915.0,
      "end_time": 322709.0,
      "text": "What will this future without secrets look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 322709.0,
      "end_time": 324673.0,
      "text": "And should we care?"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 324673.0,
      "end_time": 326564.0,
      "text": "We may like to believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 326564.0,
      "end_time": 329604.0,
      "text": "that the future with so much wealth of data"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 329604.0,
      "end_time": 332118.0,
      "text": "would be a future with no more biases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 332118.0,
      "end_time": 335701.0,
      "text": "but in fact, having so much information"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 335701.0,
      "end_time": 337892.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t mean that we will make decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 337892.0,
      "end_time": 339598.0,
      "text": "which are more objective."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 339598.0,
      "end_time": 342158.0,
      "text": "In another experiment, we presented to our subjects"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 342158.0,
      "end_time": 344404.0,
      "text": "information about a potential job candidate."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 344404.0,
      "end_time": 347582.0,
      "text": "We included in this information some references"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 347582.0,
      "end_time": 350228.0,
      "text": "to some funny, absolutely legal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 350228.0,
      "end_time": 352693.0,
      "text": "but perhaps slightly embarrassing information"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 352693.0,
      "end_time": 354712.0,
      "text": "that the subject had posted online."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 354713.0,
      "end_time": 357790.0,
      "text": "Now interestingly, among our subjects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 357790.0,
      "end_time": 360162.0,
      "text": "some had posted comparable information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 360162.0,
      "end_time": 362524.0,
      "text": "and some had not."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 362524.0,
      "end_time": 364473.0,
      "text": "Which group do you think"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 364473.0,
      "end_time": 369250.0,
      "text": "was more likely to judge harshly our subject?"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 369250.0,
      "end_time": 370982.0,
      "text": "Paradoxically, it was the group"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 370982.0,
      "end_time": 372715.0,
      "text": "who had posted similar information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 372715.0,
      "end_time": 375657.0,
      "text": "an example of moral dissonance."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 375657.0,
      "end_time": 377407.0,
      "text": "Now you may be thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 377407.0,
      "end_time": 379109.0,
      "text": "this does not apply to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 379109.0,
      "end_time": 381270.0,
      "text": "because I have nothing to hide."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 381271.0,
      "end_time": 383753.0,
      "text": "But in fact, privacy is not about"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 383753.0,
      "end_time": 387429.0,
      "text": "having something negative to hide."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 387429.0,
      "end_time": 389782.0,
      "text": "Imagine that you are the H.R. director"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 389783.0,
      "end_time": 392730.0,
      "text": "of a certain organization, and you receive résumés,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 392730.0,
      "end_time": 395203.0,
      "text": "and you decide to find more information about the candidates."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 395203.0,
      "end_time": 397662.0,
      "text": "Therefore, you Google their names"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 397663.0,
      "end_time": 399903.0,
      "text": "and in a certain universe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 399903.0,
      "end_time": 401911.0,
      "text": "you find this information."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 401911.0,
      "end_time": 406348.0,
      "text": "Or in a parallel universe, you find this information."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 406348.0,
      "end_time": 409650.0,
      "text": "Do you think that you would be equally likely"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 409650.0,
      "end_time": 411868.0,
      "text": "to call either candidate for an interview?"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 411868.0,
      "end_time": 414150.0,
      "text": "If you think so, then you are not"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 414150.0,
      "end_time": 416732.0,
      "text": "like the U.S. employers who are, in fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 416732.0,
      "end_time": 420390.0,
      "text": "part of our experiment, meaning we did exactly that."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 420390.0,
      "end_time": 423221.0,
      "text": "We created Facebook profiles, manipulating traits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 423221.0,
      "end_time": 426720.0,
      "text": "then we started sending out résumés to companies in the U.S.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 426720.0,
      "end_time": 427980.0,
      "text": "and we detected, we monitored,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 427980.0,
      "end_time": 430373.0,
      "text": "whether they were searching for our candidates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 430373.0,
      "end_time": 432205.0,
      "text": "and whether they were acting on the information"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 432205.0,
      "end_time": 434143.0,
      "text": "they found on social media. And they were."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 434143.0,
      "end_time": 436244.0,
      "text": "Discrimination was happening through social media"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 436244.0,
      "end_time": 439317.0,
      "text": "for equally skilled candidates."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 439317.0,
      "end_time": 443892.0,
      "text": "Now marketers like us to believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 443892.0,
      "end_time": 446161.0,
      "text": "that all information about us will always"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 446161.0,
      "end_time": 449434.0,
      "text": "be used in a manner which is in our favor."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 449434.0,
      "end_time": 453149.0,
      "text": "But think again. Why should that be always the case?"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 453149.0,
      "end_time": 455813.0,
      "text": "In a movie which came out a few years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 455813.0,
      "end_time": 458366.0,
      "text": "\"Minority Report,\" a famous scene"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 458366.0,
      "end_time": 460942.0,
      "text": "had Tom Cruise walk in a mall"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 460942.0,
      "end_time": 464718.0,
      "text": "and holographic personalized advertising"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 464718.0,
      "end_time": 466553.0,
      "text": "would appear around him."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 466553.0,
      "end_time": 469780.0,
      "text": "Now, that movie is set in 2054,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 469780.0,
      "end_time": 471421.0,
      "text": "about 40 years from now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 471422.0,
      "end_time": 474330.0,
      "text": "and as exciting as that technology looks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 474330.0,
      "end_time": 476976.0,
      "text": "it already vastly underestimates"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 476976.0,
      "end_time": 479116.0,
      "text": "the amount of information that organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 479116.0,
      "end_time": 481599.0,
      "text": "can gather about you, and how they can use it"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 481599.0,
      "end_time": 484997.0,
      "text": "to influence you in a way that you will not even detect."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 484997.0,
      "end_time": 487100.0,
      "text": "So as an example, this is another experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 487100.0,
      "end_time": 489373.0,
      "text": "actually we are running, not yet completed."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 489373.0,
      "end_time": 491692.0,
      "text": "Imagine that an organization has access"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 491692.0,
      "end_time": 493748.0,
      "text": "to your list of Facebook friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 493748.0,
      "end_time": 495520.0,
      "text": "and through some kind of algorithm"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 495520.0,
      "end_time": 499253.0,
      "text": "they can detect the two friends that you like the most."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 499254.0,
      "end_time": 501534.0,
      "text": "And then they create, in real time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 501534.0,
      "end_time": 504376.0,
      "text": "a facial composite of these two friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 504376.0,
      "end_time": 507445.0,
      "text": "Now studies prior to ours have shown that people"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 507445.0,
      "end_time": 510330.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t recognize any longer even themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 510330.0,
      "end_time": 512792.0,
      "text": "in facial composites, but they react"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 512792.00000000006,
      "end_time": 514909.00000000006,
      "text": "to those composites in a positive manner."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 514909.0,
      "end_time": 518323.0,
      "text": "So next time you are looking for a certain product,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 518323.0,
      "end_time": 520882.0,
      "text": "and there is an ad suggesting you to buy it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 520883.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523790.00000000006,
      "text": "it will not be just a standard spokesperson."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 523789.0,
      "end_time": 526103.0,
      "text": "It will be one of your friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 526103.0,
      "end_time": 529406.0,
      "text": "and you will not even know that this is happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 529406.0,
      "end_time": 531819.0,
      "text": "Now the problem is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 531819.0,
      "end_time": 534338.0,
      "text": "the current policy mechanisms we have"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 534338.0,
      "end_time": 537776.0,
      "text": "to protect ourselves from the abuses of personal information"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 537776.0,
      "end_time": 540760.0,
      "text": "are like bringing a knife to a gunfight."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 540760.0,
      "end_time": 543673.0,
      "text": "One of these mechanisms is transparency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 543673.0,
      "end_time": 546873.0,
      "text": "telling people what you are going to do with their data."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 546873.0,
      "end_time": 548979.0,
      "text": "And in principle, that&#39;s a very good thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 548979.0,
      "end_time": 552646.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s necessary, but it is not sufficient."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 552646.0,
      "end_time": 556343.0,
      "text": "Transparency can be misdirected."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 556344.0,
      "end_time": 558448.0,
      "text": "You can tell people what you are going to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 558448.0,
      "end_time": 560680.0,
      "text": "and then you still nudge them to disclose"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 560680.0,
      "end_time": 563303.0,
      "text": "arbitrary amounts of personal information."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 563303.0,
      "end_time": 566189.0,
      "text": "So in yet another experiment, this one with students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 566189.0,
      "end_time": 569247.0,
      "text": "we asked them to provide information"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 569247.0,
      "end_time": 571600.0,
      "text": "about their campus behavior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 571600.0,
      "end_time": 574000.0,
      "text": "including pretty sensitive questions, such as this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 574000.0,
      "end_time": 574621.0,
      "text": "[Have you ever cheated in an exam?]"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 574621.0,
      "end_time": 576920.0,
      "text": "Now to one group of subjects, we told them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 576921.0,
      "end_time": 579762.0,
      "text": "\"Only other students will see your answers.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 579762.0,
      "end_time": 581340.0,
      "text": "To another group of subjects, we told them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 581341.0,
      "end_time": 584902.0,
      "text": "\"Students and faculty will see your answers.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 584902.0,
      "end_time": 587493.0,
      "text": "Transparency. Notification. And sure enough, this worked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 587493.0,
      "end_time": 588900.0,
      "text": "in the sense that the first group of subjects"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 588900.0,
      "end_time": 591468.0,
      "text": "were much more likely to disclose than the second."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 591468.0,
      "end_time": 592988.0,
      "text": "It makes sense, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 592988.0,
      "end_time": 594478.0,
      "text": "But then we added the misdirection."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 594478.0,
      "end_time": 597238.0,
      "text": "We repeated the experiment with the same two groups,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 597238.0,
      "end_time": 599665.0,
      "text": "this time adding a delay"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 599665.0,
      "end_time": 602599.0,
      "text": "between the time we told subjects"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 602600.0,
      "end_time": 604680.0,
      "text": "how we would use their data"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 604680.0,
      "end_time": 609680.0,
      "text": "and the time we actually started answering the questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 609680.0,
      "end_time": 611629.0,
      "text": "How long a delay do you think we had to add"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 611629.0,
      "end_time": 616242.0,
      "text": "in order to nullify the inhibitory effect"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 616242.0,
      "end_time": 619652.0,
      "text": "of knowing that faculty would see your answers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 619653.0,
      "end_time": 621433.0,
      "text": "Ten minutes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 621433.0,
      "end_time": 623224.0,
      "text": "Five minutes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 623224.0,
      "end_time": 625000.0,
      "text": "One minute?"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 625000.0,
      "end_time": 627490.0,
      "text": "How about 15 seconds?"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 627490.0,
      "end_time": 629717.0,
      "text": "Fifteen seconds were sufficient to have the two groups"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 629717.0,
      "end_time": 631285.0,
      "text": "disclose the same amount of information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 631285.0,
      "end_time": 634310.0,
      "text": "as if the second group now no longer cares"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 634310.0,
      "end_time": 636686.0,
      "text": "for faculty reading their answers."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 636687.0,
      "end_time": 640230.0,
      "text": "Now I have to admit that this talk so far"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 640230.0,
      "end_time": 642503.0,
      "text": "may sound exceedingly gloomy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 642503.0,
      "end_time": 644224.0,
      "text": "but that is not my point."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 644224.0,
      "end_time": 646923.0,
      "text": "In fact, I want to share with you the fact that"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 646923.0,
      "end_time": 648695.0,
      "text": "there are alternatives."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 648695.0,
      "end_time": 651194.0,
      "text": "The way we are doing things now is not the only way"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 651194.0,
      "end_time": 654231.0,
      "text": "they can done, and certainly not the best way"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 654231.0,
      "end_time": 656258.0,
      "text": "they can be done."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 656258.0,
      "end_time": 660429.0,
      "text": "When someone tells you, \"People don&#39;t care about privacy,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 660429.0,
      "end_time": 663710.0,
      "text": "consider whether the game has been designed"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 663710.0,
      "end_time": 665795.0,
      "text": "and rigged so that they cannot care about privacy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 665795.0,
      "end_time": 669560.0,
      "text": "and coming to the realization that these manipulations occur"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 669570.0,
      "end_time": 670664.0,
      "text": "is already halfway through the process"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 670664.0,
      "end_time": 672922.0,
      "text": "of being able to protect yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 672922.0,
      "end_time": 676632.0,
      "text": "When someone tells you that privacy is incompatible"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 676632.0,
      "end_time": 678481.0,
      "text": "with the benefits of big data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 678481.0,
      "end_time": 680954.0,
      "text": "consider that in the last 20 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 680954.0,
      "end_time": 682871.0,
      "text": "researchers have created technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 682871.0,
      "end_time": 686189.0,
      "text": "to allow virtually any electronic transactions"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 686189.0,
      "end_time": 689938.0,
      "text": "to take place in a more privacy-preserving manner."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 689938.0,
      "end_time": 692492.0,
      "text": "We can browse the Internet anonymously."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 692493.0,
      "end_time": 695171.0,
      "text": "We can send emails that can only be read"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 695171.0,
      "end_time": 698880.0,
      "text": "by the intended recipient, not even the NSA."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 698880.0,
      "end_time": 701877.0,
      "text": "We can have even privacy-preserving data mining."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 701877.0,
      "end_time": 705771.0,
      "text": "In other words, we can have the benefits of big data"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 705771.0,
      "end_time": 707902.0,
      "text": "while protecting privacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 707903.0,
      "end_time": 711694.0,
      "text": "Of course, these technologies imply a shifting"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 711694.0,
      "end_time": 713240.0,
      "text": "of cost and revenues"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 713240.0,
      "end_time": 715347.0,
      "text": "between data holders and data subjects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 715347.0,
      "end_time": 718800.0,
      "text": "which is why, perhaps, you don&#39;t hear more about them."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 718800.0,
      "end_time": 722506.0,
      "text": "Which brings me back to the Garden of Eden."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 722506.0,
      "end_time": 725286.0,
      "text": "There is a second privacy interpretation"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 725286.0,
      "end_time": 727940.0,
      "text": "of the story of the Garden of Eden"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 727950.0,
      "end_time": 729191.0,
      "text": "which doesn&#39;t have to do with the issue"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 729191.0,
      "end_time": 731416.0,
      "text": "of Adam and Eve feeling naked"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 731416.0,
      "end_time": 733797.0,
      "text": "and feeling ashamed."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 733797.0,
      "end_time": 736578.0,
      "text": "You can find echoes of this interpretation"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 736578.0,
      "end_time": 739360.0,
      "text": "in John Milton&#39;s \"Paradise Lost.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 739360.0,
      "end_time": 743557.0,
      "text": "In the garden, Adam and Eve are materially content."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 743557.0,
      "end_time": 745661.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re happy. They are satisfied."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 745661.0,
      "end_time": 747954.0,
      "text": "However, they also lack knowledge"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 747954.0,
      "end_time": 749593.0,
      "text": "and self-awareness."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 749594.0,
      "end_time": 752913.0,
      "text": "The moment they eat the aptly named"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 752913.0,
      "end_time": 754206.0,
      "text": "fruit of knowledge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 754206.0,
      "end_time": 756811.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s when they discover themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 756811.0,
      "end_time": 760842.0,
      "text": "They become aware. They achieve autonomy."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 760842.0,
      "end_time": 763968.0,
      "text": "The price to pay, however, is leaving the garden."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 763968.0,
      "end_time": 767848.0,
      "text": "So privacy, in a way, is both the means"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 767849.0,
      "end_time": 770811.0,
      "text": "and the price to pay for freedom."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 770811.0,
      "end_time": 773581.0,
      "text": "Again, marketers tell us"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 773581.0,
      "end_time": 776600.0,
      "text": "that big data and social media"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 776600.0,
      "end_time": 779579.0,
      "text": "are not just a paradise of profit for them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 779579.0,
      "end_time": 782360.0,
      "text": "but a Garden of Eden for the rest of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 782360.0,
      "end_time": 783274.0,
      "text": "We get free content."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 783274.0,
      "end_time": 786397.0,
      "text": "We get to play Angry Birds. We get targeted apps."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 786397.0,
      "end_time": 789294.0,
      "text": "But in fact, in a few years, organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 789294.0,
      "end_time": 790903.0,
      "text": "will know so much about us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 790903.0,
      "end_time": 793613.0,
      "text": "they will be able to infer our desires"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 793613.0,
      "end_time": 795817.0,
      "text": "before we even form them, and perhaps"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 795817.0,
      "end_time": 798264.0,
      "text": "buy products on our behalf"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 798264.0,
      "end_time": 800538.0,
      "text": "before we even know we need them."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 800538.0,
      "end_time": 803775.0,
      "text": "Now there was one English author"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 803775.0,
      "end_time": 806819.0,
      "text": "who anticipated this kind of future"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 806820.0,
      "end_time": 808225.0,
      "text": "where we would trade away"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 808225.0,
      "end_time": 811773.0,
      "text": "our autonomy and freedom for comfort."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 811773.0,
      "end_time": 813934.0,
      "text": "Even more so than George Orwell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 813934.0,
      "end_time": 816694.0,
      "text": "the author is, of course, Aldous Huxley."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 816695.0,
      "end_time": 819549.0,
      "text": "In \"Brave New World,\" he imagines a society"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 819549.0,
      "end_time": 821720.0,
      "text": "where technologies that we created"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 821720.0,
      "end_time": 823579.0,
      "text": "originally for freedom"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 823579.0,
      "end_time": 826146.0,
      "text": "end up coercing us."
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 826146.0,
      "end_time": 830937.0,
      "text": "However, in the book, he also offers us a way out"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 830937.0,
      "end_time": 834375.0,
      "text": "of that society, similar to the path"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 834375.0,
      "end_time": 838330.0,
      "text": "that Adam and Eve had to follow to leave the garden."
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 838330.0,
      "end_time": 840477.0,
      "text": "In the words of the Savage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 840477.0,
      "end_time": 843545.0,
      "text": "regaining autonomy and freedom is possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 843546.0,
      "end_time": 846225.0,
      "text": "although the price to pay is steep."
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 846225.0,
      "end_time": 851940.0,
      "text": "So I do believe that one of the defining fights"
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 851940.0,
      "end_time": 854503.0,
      "text": "of our times will be the fight"
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 854503.0,
      "end_time": 856890.0,
      "text": "for the control over personal information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 856890.0,
      "end_time": 860396.0,
      "text": "the fight over whether big data will become a force"
    },
    {
      "index": 328,
      "start_time": 860397.0,
      "end_time": 861686.0,
      "text": "for freedom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 329,
      "start_time": 861686.0,
      "end_time": 866432.0,
      "text": "rather than a force which will hiddenly manipulate us."
    },
    {
      "index": 330,
      "start_time": 866432.0,
      "end_time": 869250.0,
      "text": "Right now, many of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 331,
      "start_time": 869250.0,
      "end_time": 871778.0,
      "text": "do not even know that the fight is going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 332,
      "start_time": 871778.0,
      "end_time": 874450.0,
      "text": "but it is, whether you like it or not."
    },
    {
      "index": 333,
      "start_time": 874450.0,
      "end_time": 877254.0,
      "text": "And at the risk of playing the serpent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 334,
      "start_time": 877254.0,
      "end_time": 880151.0,
      "text": "I will tell you that the tools for the fight"
    },
    {
      "index": 335,
      "start_time": 880151.0,
      "end_time": 883160.0,
      "text": "are here, the awareness of what is going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 336,
      "start_time": 883160.0,
      "end_time": 884515.0,
      "text": "and in your hands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 337,
      "start_time": 884515.0,
      "end_time": 888255.0,
      "text": "just a few clicks away."
    },
    {
      "index": 338,
      "start_time": 888255.0,
      "end_time": 889737.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 339,
      "start_time": 889737.0,
      "end_time": 894214.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}